casebody.data:
Gadsden D. Bryan, Plaintiff in Error, v. City of West Palm Beach, a Municipal Corporation, Defendant in Error. Price & Price and James M. Carson, for Plaintiff in Error; H. L. Bussey, for Defendant in Error.

A' Writ of Error to the Circuit Court for Palm Beach County.

Writ of Error dismissed by the Court upon suggestion of the death of the plaintiff in error.
